    stem: `A 51-year-old Aboriginal man with a history of acute pancreatitis presents with persistent abdominal pain and loss of appetite. On examination, an abdominal mass is found. A contrast abdominal CT scan is performed, one cut of which is shown in the following photograph. Which one of the following is the most likely diagnosis?`,
